g.text: legged LEDs and stickers to hold
Both versions require a #2 Safety Pin to etch with and a 5mm clear LED. We find that white, blue, and
green LEDs tend to work best We use 1/8th inch clear acrylic, but any similar thickness would work just
Parts are designed to pop into place, but they won’t stay there unless you use the additional paper clips
or stickers that each version requires.
Power with a standard CR2032 battery.
Kits can be bought at BrownDogGadgets.com. Feel free to use your own laser cutter or CNC router to
